        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 34da3df4-0d3d-4f61-91da-2a97ca739648).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47.\r\rOur client is the Carabinieri, the Italian gendarmerie. They are losing the war against the Italian mafia, and need our help. Evidence has come to light, revealing that Torres Piombo, a citizen of Sapienza, may be smuggling narcotics ffrom Colombia into Italy for the Delgado cartel. However, the evidence wouldn&apos;t hold up in court. The Carabinieri would like us to play judge, jury, and executioner, and eliminate both Piombo and his mafia contacts. I will leave you to prepare.",
